Daniel S. Loeb - Wikipedia





















 






Daniel S. Loeb

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search



Dan Loeb


Born
Daniel Seth Loeb
(1961-12-18) December 18, 1961 (age 55)
Santa Monica, California, U.S.


